@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_erolfp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v0 / (tmp - wp.exp(v0 + 1.00)))
    v1 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.72) / (tmp + 0.74 * v1 + 0.32)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.81 * v2 + 0.59)))
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.61 / v0 + 0.35) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.71)) * wp.exp((v0 + 0.80 * v2 + 0.27)))
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.09) - wp.abs(v0 + 0.15)) + v2)
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = ((0.97 + wp.exp(v2 + 0.96)) - tmp)
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
